            "title": "港股尾段倒跌4點  阿里巴巴升幅收窄至2%以下",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒指下午3:43倒跌4點或0.02%，報21853，國指跌36點或0.46%，報8021，科指跌37點或0.71%，報5243點，大市成交3427.01億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)升1.93%，報116元。阿里健康(00241)升3.41%，報4.55元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">比亞迪電子(00285)挫8.1%，報55.7元，為表現最差藍籌股。</p>\n</div>",
