            "title": "將軍澳新寶城錄2房戶580萬元易手    原業主持貨約4年帳蝕逾2成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美聯物業將軍澳新都城分行促成將軍澳新寶城本月首宗成交，用家以580萬元承接一個434實呎戶，原業主持貨約4年，帳面虧蝕約180萬元離場。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上述成交單位為將軍澳新寶城6座中層A室，實用面積約434平方呎，2房間隔。單位去年11月以628萬元放盤，其後減價至590萬元，議價後以580萬元購入單位自住，實用呎價約13,364元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">參考成交資料，原業主於2021年7月以760萬元購入上述物業，原業主持貨約4年，期內單位貶值約180萬元，或約23.7%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14703518-%e5%b0%87%e8%bb%8d%e6%be%b3%e6%96%b0%e5%af%b6%e5%9f%8e%e9%8c%842%e6%88%bf%e6%88%b6580%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%98%93%e6%89%8b-%e5%8e%9f%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%bb%e6%8c%81%e8%b2%a8%e7%b4%844%e5%b9%b4%e5%b8%b3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-13 15:20:23",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "午後波動 滬指收跌13點 深指跌0.77% 中芯A股倒跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地A股午後轉波動，滬深兩市股指齊先彈後急回，以全日低位及近低位收市；芯片股遇壓，中芯(00981)A股(688981.SH)倒跌收場。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230704-174914_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230704-174914_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早低開3點後，早市呈好淡爭持格局，半日高低位相差僅20點，午後乘著人民幣匯價向好，加上港股一度上沖，滬指也轉升並衝上3359點高位，升12點，其後港股升幅明顯收窄，滬指掉頭重新報跌，以全日低位收市；滬指收報3332點，跌13點或0.42%，成交7058億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指同樣於午後先倒升後轉跌，於尾市有試底之勢，最後以靠近低位收市；深指收報10626點，跌82點或0.77%，成交1.11萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數也跌14點或0.38%，以3905點收市；創業板指數跌15點或0.71%，報2176點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00981-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00981-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">芯片股重現壓力，中芯A股收跌3.07%，報101.11元，成交逾71億元；瑞芯微(603893.SH)曾挫8.14%，寒武紀(603893.SH)亦跌2.74%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"山西汾酒官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/600809.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"山西汾酒官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/600809.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">山西汾酒官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">早前弱勢的釀酒行業今日卻幾乎全面向好，貴州茅台(600519.SH)升幅擴大至漲22.06元或1.53%，報1465.06元；五糧液(000858.SZ)漲2.98%，報131.51元。山西汾酒(600809)飆6.75%，金種子酒(600199.SH)升幅略為收窄至6%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14703513-%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e6%b3%a2%e5%8b%95-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c13%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c0-77-%e4%b8%ad%e8%8a%afa%e8%82%a1%e5%80%92%e8%b7%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250206_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-13 15:15:30",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "平安好醫生宣布接入Deepseek  午後升逾1.9%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">平安好醫生(01833)宣布，在其「平安醫博通」多模態大模型、「平安醫家人」醫生工作台基礎上，已完成DeepSeek部署及部分場景應用驗證。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"平安好醫生官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/416x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01833_WEB_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"平安好醫生官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/416x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01833_WEB_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">平安好醫生官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">平安好醫生升1.92%，報6.36元，成交4.59億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公布稱，此次接入DeepSeek大模型，標志平安健康的AI技術體系將迎來重大升級。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">通過與平安健康現有的AI模型結合，DeepSeek將幫助公司進一步提升醫療服務的智能化水平。例如，在疾病診斷方面，DeepSeek可通過分析海量醫學數據，輔助醫生進行更精准的診斷；在健康管理方面，DeepSeek可根據用戶的健康數據，提供個性化的健康管理方案。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14703441-%e5%b9%b3%e5%ae%89%e5%a5%bd%e9%86%ab%e7%94%9f%e5%ae%a3%e5%b8%83%e6%8e%a5%e5%85%a5deepseek",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01833_WEB_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-13 15:05:22",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日出康城晉海477實呎戶593萬元沽    2018年貨帳蝕近3成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美聯物業將軍澳天晉匯分行表示，新近促成日出康城晉海的二手成交，買家以593萬元購入一個477實呎戶，原業主持貨約7年，損手逾「2球」離場。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上述成交的單位為日出康城晉海3b座中低層D室，實用面積約477平方呎，屬2房間隔。買家以593萬元承接單位自住，實用呎價約12,432元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">參考成交資料，原業主於2018年6月以827.6萬元購入上述物業，持貨約7年，是次轉手帳蝕約234.6萬元，或28.3%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14702922-%e6%97%a5%e5%87%ba%e5%ba%b7%e5%9f%8e%e6%99%89%e6%b5%b7477%e5%af%a6%e5%91%8e%e6%88%b6593%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%b2%bd-2018%e5%b9%b4%e8%b2%a8%e5%b8%b3%e8%9d%95%e8%bf%913%e6%88%90",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-13 14:55:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
